		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Staff - Very Rare (Requires Attunement by a Druid, Sorcerer, Warlock, or Wizard)</em></p><p><br />While holding the staff, you have resistance to &amp;reference[fire] damage.</p><p><strong>Activation</strong> - 10 Charges (Regains [[/r 1d8+2]] Charges at Dawn)</p><ul><li><p>While holding the staff, you can expend charges to activate one of the following magical effects using your spell save DC:</p><ul><li><p>Action (1 Charges) - <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.etJoWZwBdvTMuJwh]{Burning Hands}</em></p></li><li><p>Action (2 Charges) - <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.pbT9cw6nsjpmwrVZ]{Fireball}</em></p></li><li><p>Action (3 Charges) - <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.zQ7lBRzId8peTjor]{Wall of Fire}</em></p></li></ul></li><li><p>If you expend the last charge, roll [[/r 1d20]]. On a 1, the staff blackens, crumbles to ash, and is destroyed.</p></li></ul>",
